last_episode_to_air.name: Secrets in the Snow
last_episode_to_air.overview: After two Colorado women vanish in a deadly winter storm, key evidence keeps the case open for investigators to uncover the truth; a harrowing blizzard rescue the very same night could hold the clues to an almost 40-year search for the killer.

episodes.name: In the Name of the Father

episodes.name: Tangled Web
episodes.overview: After a young woman vanishes from her neighborhood, detectives are snared in a web of deceit.

episodes.name: Murders in Maine
episodes.overview: When a young mother goes missing, the case goes cold until another mom suddenly vanishes.

episodes.name: The Imposter
episodes.overview: A man goes missing, leaving detectives puzzled and a daughter driven to find her father.

episodes.name: Gone Girls
episodes.overview: When a man makes a disturbing discovery in a backyard beach, a series of horrifying events unfold.

episodes.name: A Deadly Plea
episodes.overview: When a long held secret in Florida exposes a deadly truth, investigators unravel a mystery.

episodes.name: New England Nightmare
episodes.overview: A murderous ripple spreads through a New England town when a ghastly discovery is made in a barn.

episodes.name: Deep in the Cornfields
episodes.overview: Federal agents descend on a tiny Ohio town after a beloved girl goes missing.

episodes.name: Fatal Secrets
episodes.overview: A couple makes a stunning discovery in the backyard; a brother appears desperate to find his sister.

episodes.name: Living in Fear
episodes.overview: A case of identity theft in the Arizona desert takes a blood curdling turn.

episodes.name: Desperate Search
episodes.overview: A southern California community is gripped by fear when one of its own vanishes without a trace.

episodes.name: He Wasn't Alone
episodes.overview: Evidence leads investigators across three state lines and to the discovery of an astounding truth.

episodes.name: Garden of Evil
episodes.overview: All is not as it seems as investigators dig into the life of a single mom.

episodes.name: Fatal Mistake
episodes.overview: A bizarre trail from South Dakota to Minnesota ends in a dark discovery and a case gone cold.

episodes.name: Blood Brothers
episodes.overview: A deadly mystery with deep running roots snakes through a small Alabama town.

episodes.name: Last Call
episodes.overview: An unsuspecting field worker makes a horrifying discovery in a backyard orchard.

episodes.name: Blood in the Backyard
episodes.overview: Bonnie Gamboa and her newborn inexplicably vanish from their California home. When blood is discovered in their backyard, a grieving father's world is flipped upside down and scrutinized. Investigators race against the clock to bring this mother and child home before it's too late, but in an astonishing twist, an unexpected suspect and a motive built around deception and lies leave investigators and family members stunned.

episodes.name: Deadly Ally
episodes.overview: A land developer disappears into the Arizona desert, and a brother sets out to uncover the truth; when hikers stumble onto a gruesome discovery, investigators quickly realize no one can be trusted when they find themselves in the line of fire.

episodes.name: Dead Girls Don't Talk
episodes.overview: A horrific discovery in a backyard cornfield is just the beginning of an unspeakable scene. As horrors unfold in this small, Midwest town, someone is playing a deadly game of cat and mouse and it will be years before a ghastly truth is revealed.

episodes.name: Devil In Our Country
episodes.overview: A pleasant Michigan day takes a dark turn when a field hand digs up a human skull in a sprawling backyard; the discovery leaves a tight-knit community shaken to its core and questioning whether a killer has penetrated the safety of its town.

episodes.name: Femme Fatale
episodes.overview: When a private investigator disappears with tens of thousands of dollars, Florida detectives question whether she's alive and well. But when a buried body is uncovered, they chase a trail of secrets and lies to catch a killer just out of reach.

episodes.name: Buried in the Woods: Grief or Guilt
episodes.overview: A beloved high school track star vanishes into the Philadelphia night and those in her innermost circle are eyed as suspects. When a terrifying scene is unearthed in the nearby woods, a family demands answers, but nobody is prepared for the truth.

episodes.name: Buried in the Woods: Friend Left Behind
episodes.overview: A party in the woods of a Pennsylvania coal-mining town takes a turn when someone goes missing.

episodes.name: Buried In The Woods: Girl In The Grave
episodes.overview: A hike in the woods of the Hollywood Hills takes a terrifying turn when a dog digs up a female foot. As panic spreads through a Southern California community a family fears for its own safety and investigators will stop at nothing to catch a killer.

episodes.name: Buried In The Woods: Deadly Premonition
episodes.overview: When a new college graduate's car is found abandoned, investigators race to find the missing girl.

episodes.name: Buried in the Woods First Love Last Breath
episodes.overview: A lovesick teen goes missing, and investigators in Indiana learn she's keeping a secret; teens make a gruesome discovery in the woods, and a local high school's dark secrets are soon revealed.

episodes.name: Buried in the House Dont Unlock the Freezer
episodes.overview: A couple makes a ghastly discovery buried in their Ohio home. And when investigators field another call, they fear someone may be preying on young women. But as suspects begin to surface, a cover-up far more sinister than the crime comes to light.

episodes.name: Under the Crawlspace
episodes.overview: A friendly bet exposes a terrifying scene under a California home.

episodes.name: Buried in the House: Last Person Inside
episodes.overview: When a concerned neighbor stumbles onto a horrifying scene in a Spokane, Washington home, a family is devastated and some buried secrets come to light. Investigators unravel a bizarre web of truths and lies to find enough evidence to catch a killer.

episodes.name: In the Dark of Night
episodes.overview: The joy of Christmas looks bright for a doting Oklahoma Mom. But her kids wake up to a living nightmare when she's inexplicably gone. As investigators track two suspects down a deceitful road, an incendiary break lures the killer out of the dark.

episodes.name: When Hell Freezes Over
episodes.overview: When the car of a Southern California girl is found abandoned, investigators spend years and travel hundreds of miles trying to solve her mysterious disappearance. Finally, an unimaginable backyard discovery by drug agents leads to a vicious killer.

episodes.name: Witness to Murder
episodes.overview: A Florida co-ed disappears after a night on the town. As investigators trace her last steps, they fear some missing girls at another campus might be connected. But when a dog sniffs out a backyard grave, the key to this mystery is far closer to home.

episodes.name: Saint and Sinner
episodes.overview: A former Catholic priest turned realtor vanishes from Florida and investigators find themselves examining circumstances stranger than their suspects. When a tip exposes a murder-for-hire scheme, the mastermind is revealed as a cold-blooded killer.

episodes.name: Fear In Florida
episodes.overview: After a real estate agent disappears, Florida investigators scrutinize the men in her life.

episodes.name: Buried in Money
episodes.overview: The luckiest moment in a man's life gives way to a dark mystery when he vanishes after winning a multi-million-dollar lottery.

episodes.name: The Bones on Party Hill
episodes.overview: A small town is rocked when a popular hostess at the town's favorite tavern disappears; neighbors in the tight-knit community eye each other suspiciously, unaware that the answers may lie beneath the rolling Nebraska Sandhills.

episodes.name: Buried in the Sand: Underneath the Sunset
episodes.overview: When the popular owner of a boutique motel on an island paradise in Florida disappears amid signs of foul play, the deadly secrets of a quaint beach town slowly work their way up through the pristine white sand.

episodes.name: Wading in the Water
episodes.overview: When a successful lawyer's body is found buried in a South Floridian canal, detectives use innovative technology to follow the gruesome steps taken by an evil killer.

episodes.name: Deep Freeze
episodes.overview: An entrepreneur forges an unlikely friendship with a ragtag group of skateboarders; but when he vanishes and signs point to foul play, police wonder whether he was really a friend or a target.

episodes.name: Buried in the Sand: A Cowboy's Final Ride
episodes.overview: A cowboy more at ease with horses than people vanishes into the desert after running into a group of California ranchers who believe he's done them wrong. Police must determine whether he rode off into the sunset or was the target of a deadly vengeance.

episodes.name: Secrets on the Side of the Road
episodes.overview: A California mom of three vanishes, and her car is found by the side of a desolate road with a suspicious flat tire. The case goes cold for years until a new detective takes on the case and is determined to get answers.

episodes.name: Buried in the Woods: Secrets of the Hollywood Hills
episodes.overview: A night out on Hollywood's notorious Sunset Strip leads to a desperate search when a teenage girl doesn't make it home. The search for answers weaves though the strange side of Los Angeles before the tragic truth is uncovered in the Hollywood Hills.

episodes.name: Deadly Teen Drama
episodes.overview: When a high school student mysteriously vanishes, police must sort through the whispers, lies, and deeply personal secrets of a group of teenagers in a small Michigan town to unearth the deadly truth.

episodes.name: Mystery at the Mine
episodes.overview: A missing young father in Utah returns home and confesses to an affair but vanishes again.

episodes.name: Deadliest of Friends
episodes.overview: A Colorado woman vanishes shortly after moving in with a group of friends.

episodes.name: A Family Affair
episodes.overview: The discovery of a body buried in a Delaware backyard launches police into a twisted investigation.

episodes.name: Gruesome Golf Course
episodes.overview: A former judge retires to Florida and becomes the center of a mystery when he vanishes.

episodes.name: A Vanishing Professor
episodes.overview: A weekend getaway becomes the center of a mystery when a respected college professor disappears.

episodes.name: Dangerous Secrets
episodes.overview: A popular librarian vanishes after a night of dancing in Kentucky's capital city.

episodes.name: Mystery Millionaire
episodes.overview: Police believe the discovery of a body in a backyard ends the desperate search for a missing woman.

episodes.name: Storm of the Century
episodes.overview: A beloved Missouri couple is thought to be swept away in a record-breaking deadly storm, but when a closer look at the family farm points to foul play, law enforcement searches for clues long since washed away.

episodes.name: Boy Witness
episodes.overview: When a Michigan mother disappears on an afternoon walk, investigators pin all hope on their sole eyewitness: a 10-year-old boy who may have witnessed the unthinkable.

episodes.name: Death in Blue
episodes.overview: When a successful Arizona businesswoman disappears on a holiday shopping trip, investigators hunt for a kidnapper; when the killer takes his secrets to the grave, however, the only chance of finding her is a psychic's mysterious vision.

episodes.name: Hundred-Foot Grave
episodes.overview: A young couple sets out from a holiday visit but never make it home as law enforcement search dangerous terrain fraught with derelict silver mines. In the black night and bitter cold, what happens when no one can hear you scream?

episodes.name: Deadly Trust
episodes.overview: A spunky grandmother and former bail bondswoman is a no-show at work, leaving friends and family desperate for answers.

episodes.name: Last Song You'll Ever Hear
episodes.overview: When a California mother wakes to find the door wide open and her daughter missing, law enforcement travel the country to find her until they discover a dark plot that began at the teen's doorstep.

episodes.name: To Catch a Thief
episodes.overview: When a widower disappears from his Southern California home, investigators find themselves caught up in a federal investigation involving the infamous hunt for skyjacker D.B. Cooper.

episodes.name: One of Our Own
episodes.overview: When a promising forensics student is found mutilated on a lonely stretch of Utah motorway, her Sheriff's department colleagues will stop at nothing to deliver justice.

episodes.name: Unlucky Gamble
episodes.overview: Detectives attempt to trace a young woman's last steps as she leaves a casino and disappears into the night. An almost forgotten childhood memory helps find her buried in the backyard.

episodes.name: Buried Again
episodes.overview: When a young South Carolina father goes missing, investigators must navigate a twisting trail of small-town rumors and misguided revenge to uncover the deadly truth.

episodes.name: Gone in the Sand
episodes.overview: When a Texas father disappears without a trace, investigators go on an international manhunt to catch a killer and unravel a sinister plot that has them searching for answers deep into the Chihuahuan Desert.

episodes.name: Poison Letters
episodes.overview: A retiree settles in Southern California hoping to live his best life; when he disappears without a trace, investigators must uncover if his demise was connected to the unconventional pen pals he made.

episodes.name: Death in Christmas Town
episodes.overview: A beloved mother is found brutally murdered near the military town of North Pole, Alaska, and soon four more girls meet the same fate.

episodes.name: Buried by the Bratva
episodes.overview: A champion Russian boxer disappears from Brighton Beach, N.Y., and the neighbourhood dare not talk for fear of reprisal until investigators uncover a long-buried secret in a New Jersey backyard.

episodes.name: Secrets in the Snow
episodes.overview: After two Colorado women vanish in a deadly winter storm, key evidence keeps the case open for investigators to uncover the truth; a harrowing blizzard rescue the very same night could hold the clues to an almost 40-year search for the killer.
